<break time="1000ms"/>

<!-- Retention Phase Round 1 -->
<p>
<s>Now, let all the air out.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>And hold. Empty.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Relax your body. No tension.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>You are fully oxygenated. There is no emergency.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Simply rest in the stillness.</s>
</p>

<break time="5000ms"/>

<p>
<s>Stay with it.</s>
<break time="5000ms"/>
<s>Notice the peace.</s>
<break time="5000ms"/>
<s>Your body knows when it needs to breathe.</s>
<break time="5000ms"/>
<s>Trust it.</s>
</p>

<break time="10000ms"/>

<p>
<s>When you feel the urge to breathe, take a deep breath in.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Fill your lungs completely.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>Now hold at the top. Squeeze gently. Feel the energy rise.</s>
<break time="5000ms"/>
<s>And release.</s>
</p>

<break time="3000ms"/>

<p>
<s>That's round one complete.</s>
<break time="1500ms"/>
<s>Take a few normal breaths.</s>
<break time="3000ms"/>
<s>Notice how you feel.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>The tingling. The lightness. The clarity.</s>
<break time="2000ms"/>
<s>This is your natural state, hidden beneath the usual noise.</s>
</p>

